{"tid":343270,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"兩個plan點揀好?","createTime":"2017-08-01T10:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T11:28:48.000Z","uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34d886005225bafe21944ef3bc04081d4e11e9d7","tid":343270,"uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:03:59.000Z","msg":"我將啲資金比咗屋企人管理,<br />\n依家有兩種plan.<br />\n<br />\nA: 自負盈虧,賺咗嗰筆錢比20%屋企人.<br />\nB: 蝕嘅屋企人貼番比我,賺咗嗰筆錢比50%屋企人.<br />\n<br />\n講番少少背景,我仲讀緊書,對投資認識唔多,本身嘅錢用屋企人戶口買咗匯控同港燈(應該都買咗一年有多),假設屋企人唔會立壞心腸推我去死,咁揀邊個plan好?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> plan a<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> plan b"},{"pid":"252e1902e5aaaec7bf092c95700dc17732184b31","tid":343270,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:07:03.000Z","msg":"買完匯控港燈仲有咩好管理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你屋企人會幫你放左佢去炒輪炒金？"},{"pid":"b74e5efd34c5c44896db043d49c25f43dc260cce","tid":343270,"uid":68993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T11:28:48.000Z","msg":"plan B 無風險"}]}